headline: GoDaddy Inc. to Present at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE: GDDY) Chief Executive Officer Aman Bhutani and Chief Financial Officer Mark McCaffrey will present at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference in San Francisco, California, on Monday, March 3, 2025, at 12:15 p.m. ET / 9:15 a.m. PT.

headline: GoDaddy: AI is a Job Creator, Not a Job Threat
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) is already reshaping America's economy, and for the first time, GoDaddy reveals how small businesses—not only tech giants—are leading the charge with measurable job creation and local growth.
